{"number":93,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" وَٱلضُّحَىٰ","translation":"By the morning brightness","transliteration":"Wadduha","page":596},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"وَٱلَّيْلِ إِذَا سَجَىٰ","translation":"And [by] the night when it covers with darkness,","transliteration":"Wallayli itha saja","page":596},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"مَا وَدَّعَكَ رَبُّكَ وَمَا قَلَىٰ","translation":"Your Lord has not taken leave of you, [O Muḥammad], nor has He detested [you].","transliteration":"Ma waddaAAaka rabbuka wama qala","page":596},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"وَلَلْـَٔاخِرَةُ خَيْرٌ لَّكَ مِنَ ٱلْأُولَىٰ","translation":"And the Hereafter is better for you than the first [life].","transliteration":"Walal-akhiratu khayrun laka minaal-oola","page":596},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"وَلَسَوْفَ يُعْطِيكَ رَبُّكَ فَتَرْضَىٰٓ","translation":"And your Lord is going to give you, and you will be satisfied.","transliteration":"Walasawfa yuAAteeka rabbuka fatarda","page":596},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"أَلَمْ يَجِدْكَ يَتِيمًا فَـَٔاوَىٰ","translation":"Did He not find you an orphan and give [you] refuge?","transliteration":"Alam yajidka yateeman faawa","page":596},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآلًّا فَهَدَىٰ","translation":"And He found you lost and guided [you],","transliteration":"Wawajadaka dallan fahada","page":596},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"وَوَجَدَكَ عَآئِلًا فَأَغْنَىٰ","translation":"And He found you poor and made [you] self-sufficient.","transliteration":"Wawajadaka AAa-ilan faaghna","page":596},{"numberInSurah":9,"arabic":"فَأَمَّا ٱلْيَتِيمَ فَلَا تَقْهَرْ","translation":"So as for the orphan, do not oppress [him].","transliteration":"Faamma alyateema fala taqhar","page":596},{"numberInSurah":10,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا ٱلسَّآئِلَ فَلَا تَنْهَرْ","translation":"And as for the petitioner, do not repel [him].","transliteration":"Waamma assa-ila falatanhar","page":596},{"numberInSurah":11,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثْ","translation":"But as for the favor of your Lord, report [it].","transliteration":"Waamma biniAAmati rabbika fahaddith","page":596}]}